    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some minor fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and handles well, though it will likely need routine maintenance like new brake pads and tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at an affordable price.",
